  "body": "## Description\r\nCurrently tasks are being spawned in various parts of the code with various exit futures. \r\n\r\nWe run into issues if one task doesn't close properly or if a tokio runtime doesn't exist in the process spawning tasks that require a tokio executor. \r\n\r\nWe should isolate all the tasks to a specific runtime and wrap the task execution around a single exit future and add some Prometheus metrics to show which tasks are running and for how long.",
